sbml2modelica.preprocessing

Class PreprocessingManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • sbml2modelica.preprocessing.PreprocessingManager
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    CompartmentPreprocessingManager, EquationPreprocessingManager, EventPreprocessingManager, FunctionPreprocessingManager, ModelPreprocessingManager, ParameterPreprocessingManager, ReactionPreprocessingManager, SpeciesPreprocessingManager, SpeciesReferencePreprocessingManager, SupportPreprocessingManager, SyntaxPreprocessingManager

    public abstract class PreprocessingManager
extends java.lang.Object
    The PreprocessingManager is the base class for all those classes whose the task is to pre-process the SBML Model in order to simplify the subsequent analysis and abstraction.
    Author:
    Maggioli Filippo

        static boolean formulaContainsVariable(org.sbml.jsbml.ASTNode formula,

        This method returns true if the given ASTNode represents a formula in which a variable with a name equals to the given String appears.
